Content.Text:
This is a hot, tropical country, after
all. You're bound to be swept up by the
summery mood.
<PAGE>
Since this is a vacation, you should
just sit back and relax. Enjoy yourself!

You can catch all sorts of fish here. If
you like fishing, this place is perfect.
Wanna try your hand at it?

The sea breeze feels great, and look at
sea and sky. I could see myself living
here.
<PAGE>
But first, I've gotta find someone nice
like you. That's gonna take a long time.

This place arouses your intellectual
curiosity. Irresistible for archeology
buffs!

What was this place built for?
<PAGE>
Some ceremony, maybe? Or for a rite to
ward off evil? Hmmmm... This place is
very intriguing.

This hieroglyphic... I've been trying to
decipher it, but I can't make head nor
tails of it.
<PAGE>
Can you read it? Please, tell me what it
means.

This garden is always so pretty, and so
relaxing, too.
<PAGE>
If I had a garden like this then I don't
think I'd ever leave home!

I love the sound of the bamboo fountain
in this pond.
<PAGE>
It blends perfectly with the garden, and
the sound itself is very soothing.

When I come to this garden, I end up
gazing at the scenery. Conversation
takes a back seat!
<PAGE>
It's true what they say about beauty
being able to render you speechless.

I know. Take this home as a souvenir of
your trip. I'm sure it'll come in handy.
